<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag '_error', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', "data-turbolinks-track": "reload"%>
    <%= javascript_pack_tag 'application', "data-turbolinks-track": "reload" %>  
    <title>404 Not Found</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <article>
            <h1>404 Not Found</h1>
            <p>Sepertinya tautan yang Anda klik rusak, <br> atau halaman berikut sudah dihapus dari server kami</p>
            <form action="/">
                <button class="error-button">Ke Beranda</button>
            </form>
        </article>
        <footer><%= image_tag 'logo_dr.png' %></footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>